Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.51,0:00:02.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出事了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.30,0:00:05.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,關係和睦的夫婦居然吵架了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.51,0:00:08.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為毛啊
